# Dogs

## A Field Guide to Humanity's Best Friend

The Dog Defense Committee · 2026

<!-- note: Open by asking how many people grew up with a dog. The hands tell you what kind of audience you have — childhood-dog people will let you get away with sentimentality, dog-skeptics need the science up front. -->
