# Hunting Prowess

How dogs stack up against the rest of the predator world.

| Predator        | Success Rate | Notes                          |
|-----------------|--------------|--------------------------------|
| Lion            | ~25%         | Group hunters                  |
| Wolf            | ~14%         | Stamina pursuit                |
| **Wolf pack**   | **~38%**     | **Cooperation pays off**       |
| African wild dog| ~67%         | Highest of any large predator  |
| House cat       | ~32%         | (for comparison)               |
| Domestic dog    | varies       | Bred away from solo predation  |

<!-- note: The African wild dog number is the surprise. Most people guess lion. Lean into the cooperation angle — it's why packs win. -->
<!-- ai: parallel structure with cats.slides slide 5. notice that the cat deck claims house cat = 32%; this deck lists cats for comparison. The two decks should agree on shared facts — if you change cats.slides, double-check this slide. -->

