# Adopt, Don't Shop

Three things to do this week.

- **Volunteer at a local shelter.** Even a few hours of socialization makes shelter dogs more adoptable.
<!-- pause -->
- **Foster, don't buy.** Foster networks save more lives per dollar than any other welfare intervention.
<!-- pause -->
- **Spay, neuter, microchip.** The single most effective dog welfare intervention at population scale.

<!-- note: End slow. The shelter call-to-action is the closing — let it land. Don't rush to "thank you." -->
